'''Tulio Halperín Donghi''' (27 October 1926 – 14 November 2014) was an Argentine historian. He obtained a Ph.D in history and a law degree at the [[University of Buenos Aires]], then taught at the institution's Faculty of Arts. from 1955-1966. Donghi moved to the [[National University of the Litoral]], where he was named dean. Donghi later taught at the [[University of Oxford]], and became a faculty member of the [[University of California, Berkeley]] in 1972.<ref>{{cite news|title=Murió Tulio Halperín Donghi|url=http://www.pagina12.com.ar/diario/ultimas/20-259851-2014-11-14.html|accessdate=16 November 2014|publisher=[[Página/12]]|date=14 November 2014|language=Spanish}}</ref><ref>Iván Jaksić, "Tulio Halperin Donghi" in ''Encyclopedia of Latin American History and Culture'', vol. 3, p. 171. New York: Charles Scribner's Sons 1996.</ref>
==Biography== Halperín Donghi was born in [[Buenos Aires]], in 1926. He received both a ''[[juris doctor]]'' and a Doctorate in History from the [[University of Buenos Aires]] in 1955. Halperín became a renowned [[Latin America]]n historian.
Exiled in 1966 following the ''[[La Noche de los Bastones Largos|Night of the Big Batons]]'', he divided his time between the [[University of California]] and the [[University of Buenos Aires]]. Halperín was given an award for Scholarly Distinction from the [[American Historical Association]] in 1998,<ref>[http://socrates.berkeley.edu:7001/Events/index.html Spring 2008 Calendar of Events] {{webarchive|url=https://web.archive.org/web/20080501091432/http://socrates.berkeley.edu:7001/Events/index.html |date=2008-05-01 }}, Center for Latin American Studies, University of California, Berkeley.</ref> and authored numerous books.
==Books== *''[https://books.google.com/books?id=UeKbsqzwDjAC&dq=Un+conflicto+nacional:+moriscos+y+cristianos+viejos+en+Valencia&source=gbs_navlinks_s Un conflicto nacional: moriscos y cristianos viejos en Valencia]'', 1957 {{ISBN|9788437084121}} *''[https://books.google.com/books?id=b1oNAAAAYAAJ&q=Tradici%C3%B3n+pol%C3%ADtica+espa%C3%B1ola+e+ideolog%C3%ADa+revolucionaria+de+Mayo&dq=Tradici%C3%B3n+pol%C3%ADtica+espa%C3%B1ola+e+ideolog%C3%ADa+revolucionaria+de+Mayo&hl=en&sa=X&ei=R-VnVOyPGJCryATTgoKYBQ&ved=0CCAQ6AEwAA Tradición política española e ideología revolucionaria de Mayo]'', 1961 *''[https://books.google.com/books?id=OFpCnQEACAAJ&dq=Historia+contempor%C3%A1nea+de+Am%C3%A9rica+Latina&hl=en&sa=X&ei=f-VnVOL7CMqSyASLs4DIDg&ved=0CCAQ6AEwAA Historia contemporánea de América Latina]'', 1967 {{ISBN|9788420676135}} ([https://www.google.com/search?q=Un+conflicto+nacional%3A+moriscos+y+cristianos+viejos+en+Valencia&btnG=Search+Books&tbm=bks&tbo=1&gws_rd=ssl#tbm=bks&q=editions%3AkgQVasdxPZ8C other editions] *''[https://books.google.com/books?id=EgFrQgAACAAJ&dq=El+R%C3%ADo+de+la+Plata+al+comenzar+el+siglo+XIX&hl=en&sa=X&ei=lOVnVOzLJ4P9yQS03oDgDA&ved=0CB8Q6AEwAA El Río de la Plata al comenzar el siglo XIX]'', 1961 *''[https://books.google.com/books?id=YZc4AAAAMAAJ&q=Historia+de+la+Universidad+de+Buenos+Aires&dq=Historia+de+la+Universidad+de+Buenos+Aires&hl=en&sa=X&ei=4ehnVJ-ZF8KKyATw5IKgCg&ved=0CE8Q6AEwBQ Historia de la Universidad de Buenos Aires]'', 1962 *''[https://books.google.com/books?id=AQ7qPQAACAAJ&dq=Revoluci%C3%B3n+y+Guerra:+Formaci%C3%B3n+de+una+%C3%A9lite+dirigente+en+la+Argentina+criolla&hl=en&sa=X&ei=DelnVKzZMY3-yQTqwIFA&ved=0CB0Q6AEwAA Revolución y Guerra: Formación de una élite dirigente en la Argentina criolla]'', 1972 {{ISBN|9789871220236}} *''[https://books.google.com/books?id=wdeInQEACAAJ&dq=The+Aftermath+of+Revolution+in+Latin+America&hl=en&sa=X&ei=pelnVIH7E4__yQTYuIHoCg&ved=0CB8Q6AEwAA The Aftermath of Revolution in Latin America]'' (translation of ''Hispanoamérica después de la independencia''), 1973 *''[https://books.google.com/books?id=jUVMPgAACAAJ&dq=Politics,+Economics+and+Society+in+Argentina+in+the+Revolutionary+Period&hl=en&sa=X&ei=jehnVOaLCcH4yQSZqYCQBg&ved=0CCwQ6AEwAQ Politics, Economics and Society in Argentina in the Revolutionary Period]'' (translation of ''Revolución y Guerra''), 1975 {{ISBN|9780521109031}} *''[https://books.google.com/books?id=qOXOmQEACAAJ&dq=inauthor:%22Tulio+Halper%C3%ADn+Donghi%22&hl=en&sa=X&ei=muVnVO24EZKLyATPlYCQCA&ved=0CDwQ6AEwBg La democracia de masas]'', 1991 *''[https://books.google.com/books?id=HLh7JQZhLGMC&dq=inauthor:%22Tulio+Halper%C3%ADn+Donghi%22&source=gbs_navlinks_s The Contemporary History of Latin America]'' (translation of ''Historia de América Latina''), 1993 {{ISBN|9780822313748}} *''[https://books.google.com/books?id=uu2J6FWFr0MC&dq=Proyecto+y+construcci%C3%B3n+de+una+Naci%C3%B3n&source=gbs_navlinks_s Proyecto y construcción de una Nación]'', 1996 {{ISBN|9788466000390}} *''[https://books.google.com/books?id=KWkkAQAAIAAJ&q=Son+Memorias&dq=Son+Memorias&hl=en&sa=X&ei=Q-pnVJDMG9G3yATihYHwDw&ved=0CCsQ6AEwAA Son Memorias]'', 2008 {{ISBN|9789871220908}} * [https://books.google.com/books?id=80rjAAAAMAAJ&q=inauthor:%22Tulio+Halper%C3%ADn+Donghi%22&dq=inauthor:%22Tulio+Halper%C3%ADn+Donghi%22&hl=en&sa=X&ei=muVnVO24EZKLyATPlYCQCA&ved=0CEcQ6AEwCA La Argentina y la Tormenta Del Mundo: Ideas e Ideologías Entre 1930 y 1945] {{ISBN|9789871105311}}
